  "items": [
    {
      "id": "EX-01",
      "stem_markdown": "**例题 1（热身）** 若 \\(Y_i\\) i.i.d. \\(\\mathrm{Bernoulli}(p)\\)，给出 \\(p\\) 的无偏估计并写出 \\(E[\\hat p]=p\\) 的一步验证。",
      "targets_question_types": ["short_answer"],
      "disciplines": ["statistics"],
      "topics": ["unbiased_estimator", "bernoulli"],
      "difficulty_band": "introductory",
      "related_problem_ids": ["A1"],
      "solution": {
        "final_answer_markdown": "\\(\\hat p = \\bar{Y}\\)，\\(E[\\bar{Y}] = p\\)。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "step_id": "EX01-s1",
            "detail_markdown": "取 \\(\\hat p = \\frac{1}{n}\\sum_i Y_i\\)。则 \\(E[\\hat p]=\\frac{1}{n}\\sum_i E[Y_i]=\\frac{1}{n}\\cdot np=p\\)。",
            "reasoning_tags": ["expectation_linearity"]
          }
        ],
        "verification": {
          "methods": ["algebraic_recheck"],
          "notes_markdown": "核对 Bernoulli 均值。"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "EX-02",
      "stem_markdown": "**例题 2（热身）** 将 4 个不同球放入 3 个 **有序** 盒子且 **每盒至少一球**，求方案数（数值答案）。",
      "targets_question_types": ["computation"],
      "disciplines": ["pure_mathematics"],
      "topics": ["combinatorics", "surjection"],
      "difficulty_band": "intermediate",
      "related_problem_ids": ["A2"],
      "solution": {
        "final_answer_markdown": "36。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "step_id": "EX02-s1",
            "detail_markdown": "这是 \\(n=4,k=3\\) 的「有序盒子、非空」情形，计数为 \\(3!\\,S(4,3)\\)。已知 \\(S(4,3)=6\\)（把 4 元集分成 3 个非空块的分拆数），故 \\(6\\times 6=36\\)。也可用容斥：\\(\\sum_{j=0}^3 (-1)^{3-j}\\binom{3}{j} j^4 = 36\\)。",
            "reasoning_tags": ["stirling", "inclusion_exclusion"]
          }
        ],
        "verification": {
          "methods": ["numerical_spot_check", "code_reproduction"],
          "notes_markdown": "与容斥公式或枚举程序对照。"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
